sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>15006/TCP mTLS
    participant HTTP as AutoGluon HTTP Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as AutoGluon gRPC Server<br/>8081/TCP gRPC
    participant Factory as Predictor Factory
    participant Tabular as TabularPredictor<br/>(in-process)
    participant TimeSeries as TimeSeriesPredictor<br/>(in-process)
    participant Storage as kserve-storage<br/>(in-process)
    participant S3 as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Model Loading from Storage (startup)
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Storage->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM / GCP SA credentials
        S3-->>Storage: Model files
        Storage->>Factory: Write to /mnt/models
        Factory->>Factory: Auto-detect predictor type<br/>(try TimeSeriesPredictor first,<br/>fallback to TabularPredictor)
        alt TimeSeriesPredictor detected
            Factory->>TimeSeries: Load model
        else TabularPredictor detected
            Factory->>Tabular: Load model
        end
    end

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Tabular Inference (V2 Open Inference Protocol)
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token or mTLS
        Gateway->>Istio: Forward request<br/>mTLS STRICT
        Istio->>HTTP: HTTP/8080<br/>plaintext (within mesh)
        HTTP->>Factory: Route to model
        Factory->>Tabular: predict(payload)<br/>tensor inputs → DataFrame
        Tabular-->>Factory: Prediction result
        Factory-->>HTTP: InferResponse (tensors)
        HTTP-->>Istio: JSON Response
        Istio-->>Gateway: mTLS
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response
    end

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Time Series Forecasting (V1 REST)
    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token or mTLS
        Gateway->>Istio: Forward request<br/>mTLS STRICT
        Istio->>HTTP: HTTP/8080<br/>plaintext (within mesh)
        HTTP->>Factory: Route to model
        Factory->>TimeSeries: predict(payload)<br/>JSON instances → TimeSeriesDataFrame
        TimeSeries-->>Factory: Forecast result
        Factory-->>HTTP: JSON predictions
        HTTP-->>Istio: JSON Response
        Istio-->>Gateway: mTLS
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response
    end

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: gRPC Inference (V2 Protocol)
    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Client->>Gateway: gRPC ModelInfer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token or mTLS
        Gateway->>Istio: Forward request<br/>mTLS STRICT
        Istio->>GRPC: gRPC/8081<br/>plaintext (within mesh)
        GRPC->>Factory: Route to model
        Factory->>Tabular: predict(payload)
        Tabular-->>Factory: Prediction result
        Factory-->>GRPC: InferResponse (protobuf)
        GRPC-->>Istio: gRPC Response
        Istio-->>Gateway: mTLS
        Gateway-->>Client: gRPC Response
    end
